title.narrative: Fund Cite: FY16 Program Activities:Bangkok, Thaila. Miscellaneous/Other Contractual Services - Other Contractual Services NOC (A, B, C) (ITA) (INS) (FAS). ATA TZ15CRT01 TANZANIA CRT 3. SURCHARGE FOR PR5331010. Tanaka Masami NMN-post assignment charges-NAO

description.narrative: Combat transnational terrorism, especially from al-Qa'ida, its affiliates, and adherents using a strategic counterterrorism approach that focuses on 1) countering violent extremism; 2) building the capacity of civilian law enforcement and criminal justice institutions to address threats within their own borders; and 3) building stronger relationships with our partners around the world – in order to engage in a broader, more comprehensive counterterrorism effort that treats civilian institutions, to include the justice sector and law enforcement, as a critical part of building effective partner capacity to counter terrorism.

This award strives to combat transnational terrorism, counter violent extremism, build the capacity of civilian law enforcement and criminal justice institutuions, and build stronger relationships with our partners around the world. This includes NON-PROLIFERATION[Covers miscellaneous contractual services not otherwise classified under Miscellaneous/Other Contractual Services.]. Covers miscellaneous contractual services not otherwise classified under Miscellaneous/Other Contractual Services..
